                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;running cassandra-cli with a --file argument which does not exist returns success:&lt;br/&gt;
ubuntu@host:~$ cassandra-cli --file does-not-exist ; echo $?&lt;br/&gt;
does-not-exist (No such file or directory)&lt;br/&gt;
0&lt;/p&gt;</description>
